# 五、核心模块实现规范（逐个必须实现）

---

# 1️⃣ Orchestrator（系统总控）

---

## 作用

统一控制系统流程（核心入口）

---

## 标准流程

```
输入 → 计划 → 执行 → 分析 → 预测 → 评分 → 决策 → 规则过滤 → 执行 → 输出
```

---

## 标准实现

```python
def run_agent(query, context):
    plan = planner.create_plan(query)
    results, memory = executor.execute(plan, context)

    risks = risk_engine.detect(memory)
    forecast = forecast_engine.run(memory)
    score = scoring_engine.score(context)

    decisions = decision_engine.make(memory, risks, forecast, score)
    decisions = rule_engine.filter(decisions, context)

    action_engine.execute_batch(decisions)

    report = report_builder.build(memory, risks, forecast, decisions)

    return {
        "report": report,
        "risks": risks,
        "forecast": forecast,
        "score": score,
        "decisions": decisions
    }
```

